Available 6/15/22. Bright and spacious 2 bedroom/ 2 bathroom condo. Covered parking, controlled access building. Fireplace with tile accents, balcony. Stainless appliances, tile in entry and kitchen. Very large bedroom spaces. Master suite! Washer and dryer included. 12 month minimum term, 1st month's rent and refundable deposit. no smoking and no pets. Agent to view

No pets, no smoking, please use our forms and applications. Don't apply through this site. Credit screening, income verification and references required
